Program: The Why Factor
Title: Running
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01nqywh
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 6 Jan 2014
Running is experiencing an explosion in popularity in the UK and across the world. So why are we running now more than ever - the recession, the Olympic competitive factor, the new social media app revolution, public health awareness, mid-life crises or rising life expectancy? Mike Williams, not exactly a natural runner, tests out these theories and is persuaded to try barefoot running himself. Show less